{"tid":2278883,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★突破盲點！iPhone 12會對一些帶有RFID 晶片的卡片進行「消磁」","createTime":"2020-11-09T11:58:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-09T13:22:50.000Z","uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ab2962b4ed6f4582f9775b82f8133d6ee4f58797","tid":2278883,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T11:58:01.000Z","msg":"大家都知道 iPhone 12 背後新增了一圈吸鐵石用於吸附 MagSafe 給 iPhone 吸付充電，而在日常中發現會對一些帶有磁帶或 RFID 晶片的卡片進行「消磁」，而 Apple 公司給出的方案則是讓消費者無奈了， Apple 建議這類卡片可使用 MagSafe 皮革卡包存放，內部做了屏蔽處理，這無疑反向推銷自家的周邊產品。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://qooah.com/2020/11/09/iphone-12-issues-appear/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2F2020%2F11%2F09%2Fiphone-12-issues-appear%2F&d=FEHxtXJUwAnPMx50BANU%2BegAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=67b7c51c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://qooah.com/2020/11/09/iphone-12-issues-appear/</a>"},{"pid":"e408092a8b388faa22320ba03d99568ea43776c1","tid":2278883,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T11:58:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be362a2c05d47e906e91bd680f30ea9dc26bae50","tid":2278883,"uid":3342,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T11:59:43.000Z","msg":"可以消埋將身分證？"},{"pid":"9b7baaeaeeb48a144e3df0c18af0b5efd4beb558","tid":2278883,"uid":164092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"be362a2c05d47e906e91bd680f30ea9dc26bae50","tid":2278883,"uid":3342,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T11:59:43.000Z","msg":"可以消埋將身分證？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T12:00:30.000Z","msg":"Big Brain🤯🤯"},{"pid":"55bbe925ee587f29984251ed24413